1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,500
ほしのこえ (Hoshi no koe)
[Voices of distant star]
Based on script by Tonbo (http://www.maijar.org/word/star1.htm)

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:06,500
Compiled by よ-group
